# Implementation Plan - Business Rules (3-Day Limit & Destination)

## Goal Description
1.  **3-Day Removal Rule**: Track how long a ship has been at the landing port. Soil must be removed within 3 days. Display the elapsed time and alert if it exceeds the limit.
2.  **Destination Consistency**: Since soil from one ship goes to a single landfill, linking a dump truck to a ship should automatically set the truck's destination to match the ship's destination.

